KNOWN BUGS

07.10.01
When generating a path element by directly inputing the string data
the path definition (d=>'M 1 1 L 2 2...'), rather than the hash output of the
get_path method, the string must contain no new-line characters.

09.10.01 Does not support the path element d definition 'A' or 'a'
SUPPORT

More information is available from

http://roasp.com


